item.description:
@lothy wrote:

I didn’t actually set the title to what it currently is. That was someone else’s doing.

In hindsight I realise that my post above (in reply to Kozy’s) was a little off balance.
I’m not saying that people aren’t free to develop their cheats and cheat in various servers.
I’m not saying you can’t share them, either.

What I am saying that is this Runescape Classic section does not provide provisions for cheating.
I simply don’t want people posting bots here because they are out of place.
